        <ProductSection padding="small">
          <section id="comparison-interactive">
            <h2>OpenVPN vs. Modern WireGuard® Architecture</h2>
            <p>See how Defguard's WireGuard-based solution compares to legacy OpenVPN. Select a topic to explore the differences.</p>
            
