                <div class="tab-pane active" data-content="performance">
                  <div class="comparison-split">
                    <div class="comparison-item legacy">
                      <h3>OpenVPN Performance</h3>
                      <p>OpenVPN runs in userspace, requiring data to pass between kernel and application space for every packet. This creates significant overhead.</p>
                      <ul>
                        <li>Runs in userspace (slow context switching)</li>
                        <li>100,000+ lines of code to process</li>
                        <li>Multi-second connection establishment</li>
                        <li>Drops connection on network changes</li>
                      </ul>
