                      <h3>Defguard + WireGuard® Performance</h3>
                      <p>WireGuard operates directly in the kernel with a minimal, audited codebase. Packets never leave kernel space during encryption.</p>
                      <ul>
                        <li>Runs in kernel space (zero context switching)</li>
                        <li>~4,000 lines of auditable code</li>
                        <li>Sub-100ms connection establishment</li>
                        <li>Seamless roaming between networks</li>
                      </ul>
